Setup the environment
clear

Set the loop counter in Cell zero to fifty using bulk arithmetic
passion passion passion passion passion

Initialize A in Cell one to zero
hold forget

Initialize B in Cell two to one
hold forget adore

Initialize Temp in Cell three to zero
hold forget

Return to Cell zero to start the main loop
release release release

promise
    Move to Cell one and print the current Fibonacci number natively
    hold confess

    Take a dramatic one second pause
    breathe

    Shift A into Temp
    promise
        miss
        hold hold adore
        release release
    always

    Shift B into both A and Temp
    hold
    promise
        miss
        release adore
        hold hold adore
        release
    always

    Shift Temp back into B
    hold
    promise
        miss
        release adore
        hold
    always

    Return pointer to Cell zero and decrement the loop counter
    release release release
    miss
always

Terminate the process gracefully
fade